#*: Being a soldier's wife isn't all '''beer and skittles'''.
#* '''2012''' Mar. 24, John Walsh, "[http://www.independent.co.uk/voices/columnists/john-walsh/john-walsh-the-perils-of-reviewing-restaurants--think-of-us-dear-reader-7584107.html The perils of reviewing restaurants]," ''The Independent'' (UK) <small>(retrieved 24 July 2015)</small>:
#*: His plight reveals a truth that's often obscured by the envy of newspaper readers; that it's not all '''beer and skittles''' in restaurant-critic land.

====Usage notes====
